name: Kaadu (V)
Lore: 'Used by many Gungan warriors due to their fearless nature. Kaadu lay large numbers of eggs to compensate for those eaten by predators.',
Text: 'May add 1 ''rider'' (passenger).  Ability = 1/2.  While ridden by a Beast-Rider, power and maneuver +2, cannot be attacked, your Force drains here are +1, and Kaadu and ''rider'' are immune to attrition < 4.',
